node.text: Happy 4th of July …. A very special day for our country and especially for our very large family …. This year, not able to spend it with my family and friends BUT holding court with my number one and my mother makes another country away from home feel just right.  We get bubbles instead of fireworks today !!! #bubbleswork

node.text: If work isn’t fun, then you’re doing it WRONG!! Make life smile 😎 #camprenner

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jeremy Renner on June 22, 2021. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Summer is officially here …. A lot of places in the world have opened up , but there are still many places facing difficulties in this pandemic  I want you wish you all a happy and healthy summer.  Stay safe #blessings🙏

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jeremy Renner on June 20, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 1 person, walking, standing and outdoors.

node.text: Thank you dad for setting the bar so high for me to become the best Father I can be …. And to my sweet darlin Ava, you will ALWAYS be, “The Best Part of Me”. #fathersday #bestpartofme🎼
